title: SWORD 01-05 (2010, Complete, Dgtl, Minutemen-Dts)
description: Follow the exploits of Abigal Brand and her outer space strike team in S.W.O.R.D.! This terrific mini was written by Kieron Gillen and deals with the Sentient World Observation and Response Department, first seen in the pages of Astonishing X-Men. This was supposed to be an ongoing series but didn't sell too well; Still, what we got was a great expansion on the extraterrestrial counterterrorism team. All credit to Minutemen for the scans, please seed and enjoy! :-)
